data.description: Best buy! There are a ton of original wood trim and doors. One unit painted trim and the other natural. 2 bedrooms 1st flr and 3 bedrooms in 2nd flr unit and a formal dining room. Large kitchen and spacious bedrooms and large bathrooms. Basement bath rough-in. Hardwood flrs throughout and a 2 car garage. 1st flr rented for $1025 but much more after rehab. 5 year tenant in place. Huge basement with tall ceilings. Don't let all the stuff scare you away. Call for your private showing.
